<div class="title">Prefer to enter key figures by hand?</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Do you want to enter the weight and purchase price for item bundles yourself? Do not check any of the boxes in the <strong>Bundle</strong> area, if you’d prefer to enter the data manually. If none of the boxes are checked, then the key figures for individual components won’t have any influence on the key figures for the item bundle.</p>
</div>
</td>
