<p>It’s possible to sell item sets in the <a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/en/plugins/sales/online-shops/ceres_4697">Ceres 5</a>&nbsp;<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-external-link  "></i></span> plentyShop.
